%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20moved%20to%20the%20US%2015%20years%20ago%20and%20have%20been%20almost%20exclusively%20traveling%20with%20American%20Airlines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20even%20have%20the%20company's%20credit%20card%20to%20rack%20up%20more%20miles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20family%20traveled%20to%20Italy%20on%20Lufthansa%2C%20and%20the%20experience%20was%20so%20superior.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20from%20Argentina%20to%20the%20US%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20American%20Airlines%20was%20the%20only%20one%20offering%20an%20overnight%2C%20non-stop%20flight%20from%20New%20York%2C%20where%20I%20was%20living%2C%20to%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20where%20my%20family%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20my%20go-to%20airline%20because%20of%20it.%20I%20racked%20up%20miles%20and%20status%20and%20even%20got%20their%20AAdvantage%20credit%20card%20to%20get%20more%20perks.%20When%20my%20kids%20were%20born%2C%20I%20immediately%20got%20them%20their%20own%20profiles%20so%20they%2C%20too%2C%20could%20start%20accumulating%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20flight%20on%20Lufthansa%20made%20me%20reevaluate%20my%20decision%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20that%20there%20may%20be%20better%20airlines%20for%20traveling%20with%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d038d66a-8f43-4eb1-a1da-539fb3150d77%5C%22%3EWe%20boarded%20before%20everyone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20fly%20with%20kids%20ages%205%20and%20under%20on%20Lufthansa%2C%20you%20are%20automatically%20assigned%20%26quot%3BPRE%26quot%3B%20as%20your%20boarding%20group.%20This%20means%20your%20family%20is%20allowed%20to%20preboard%20before%20everyone%2C%20giving%20parents%20extra%20time%20to%20get%20everyone%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Empty%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68640c6985e81483682d221a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EParents%20of%20kids%205%20and%20under%20can%20preboard%20on%20Lufthansa.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20are%207%2C%205%2C%20and%205%2C%20and%20on%20a%20recent%20trip%20from%20Boston%20to%20Munich%2C%20we%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20preboarding.%20I%20really%20appreciated%20this%20because%20we%20were%20traveling%20with%20carry-ons%20only%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20stress%20about%20finding%20overhead%20space%20for%20five%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20had%20time%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20was%20sitting%20where%20(my%20kids%20love%20to%20argue%20over%20the%20window%20seat)%2C%20and%20get%20their%20stuffed%20animals%20and%20snacks%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20American%20Airlines%20status%20allows%20me%20to%20board%20with%20Group%204%2C%20I%20always%20wonder%20if%20we'll%20have%20space%20for%20our%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251d5f66b-360f-4f2f-8175-b0b6d4842c22%5C%22%3EThe%20flight%20attendants%20went%20above%20and%20beyond%20for%20my%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20oldest%20has%20been%20traveling%20since%20he%20was%203%20months%20old%2C%20so%20we%20are%20pretty%20used%20to%20flying%20with%20kids.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20flight%20attendants%20at%20Lufthansa%20surprised%20me%20by%20how%20much%20they%20did%20for%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20our%20connections%2C%20my%20kids%20were%20greeted%20with%20stuffed%20animals%20and%20games%20for%20the%20plane.%20They%20each%20got%20one%2C%20and%20they%20were%20all%20age-appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20another%20flight%2C%20the%20flight%20attendants%20were%20giving%20chocolates%20to%20the%20passengers%20as%20we%20were%20landing.%20When%20they%20saw%20me%20with%20three%20little%20kids%2C%20they%20just%20dumped%20half%20the%20basket%20on%20my%20tray%20and%20smiled%20%E2%80%94%20those%20chocolates%20came%20in%20handy%20later%20in%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lufthansa%20chocolates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68640e14f748d8c055f4bb4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Airlines%20offers%20cookies%20that%20my%20kids%20love.%20I%20once%20asked%20the%20flight%20attendant%20if%20we%20could%20have%20extra%20packages%20to%20avoid%20meltdowns%20and%20was%20given%20a%20cold%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263b6bb35-aa3c-4fd2-91b2-94c3617048a8%5C%22%3EWe%20were%20all%20seated%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20the%20cheapest%20tickets%20on%20Lufthansa%20only%20to%20then%20realize%20that%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20for%20our%20seats.%20I%20paid%20about%20%24400%20for%20our%20longest%20flights%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20were%20sitting%20together%2C%20and%20left%20the%20shorter%20connections%20up%20to%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20both%20flights%2C%20we%20were%20all%20sitting%20together%20and%20in%20priority%20rows%2C%20which%20was%20key%20to%20deplane%20with%20little%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20status%20at%20American%20Airlines%2C%20we%20get%20to%20choose%20our%20seats%20for%20free%2C%20and%20haven't%20had%20an%20issue%20sitting%20together.%20There%20was%20only%20one%20time%2C%20in%202023%2C%20when%20our%20plane%20was%20changed%2C%20and%20the%20company%20sat%20my%20then-2-year-old%20son%20alone%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20plane.%20We%20were%20those%20parents%20excusing%20ourselves%20and%20asking%20people%20to%20change%20seats%20with%20us%2C%20even%20though%20we%20had%20taken%20the%20steps%20prior%20to%20ensure%20we%20were%20seated%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8dd46e2-9168-4c68-8abe-19a2a24dbe94%5C%22%3EI'm%20questioning%20my%20exclusivity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20trip%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20fully%20compare%20both%20airlines%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20everything%20ran%20so%20smoothly%20(and%20without%20delays)%20is%20making%20me%20question%20my%20exclusivity%20with%20one%20airline.%20especially%20now%20that%20other%20airlines%20offer%20the%20non-stop%20flight%20to%20Argentina%20that%20I%20am%20absolutely%20married%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%20I%20plan%20a%20family%20trip%2C%20I%20am%20more%20willing%20to%20go%20with%20other%2C%20more%20family-friendly%20airlines%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20sticking%20to%20what%20I've%20done%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20American%20Airlines%20updated%20its%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com%2Fi18n%2Fcustomer-service%2Fsupport%2Fcustomer-service-plan.jsp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ecustomer%20service%20policy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20in%20March%202023.%20The%20updated%20policy%20states%20that%20children%2014%20and%20under%20will%20be%20seated%20next%20to%20an%20accompanying%20adult%20at%20no%20additional%20cost%2C%20so%20long%20as%20certain%20conditions%20are%20met.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20American%20Airlines%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELufthansa's%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lufthansa.com%2Fde%2Fen%2Fflying-with-small-children.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ecustomer%20service%20policy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20states%20that%20they%20will%20do%20their%20best%20to%20seat%20children%20between%202%20and%2011%20next%20to%20an%20adult%20traveling%20in%20the%20same%20group%2C%20free%20of%20charge.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20rep%20for%20the%20company%20replied%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20inquiry%20about%20pre-boarding%20for%20families%20with%20the%20following%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BLufthansa%20does%20offer%20pre-boarding%20for%20families%20traveling%20with%20children%2C%20including%20both%20short-haul%20and%20long-haul%20routes.%20Families%20with%20children%2C%20group%20travelers%20and%