%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhudson-river-trading-hrt-8-billion-trading-revenue-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20proprietary%20trading%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20produced%20%248%20billion%20in%20net%20trading%20revenue%20in%202024%2C%20and%20Iain%20Dunning%2C%20an%20ex-DeepMind%20researcher%2C%20has%20led%20its%20AI%20lab%20since%202018.%20Hiring%20Villagra%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20HRT%20for%2015%20years%2C%20and%20her%20team%20isn't%20a%20coincidence%2C%20one%20quant%20recruiter%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20client%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20somebody%20like%20Julia%20there%2C%20she%20was%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20ascension%20of%20Hudson%20River%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20understands%20the%20talent%20flow%20and%20who%20built%20key%20systems.%20(Hudson%20River%20Trading%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20said%20several%20of%20its%20top-performing%20researchers%20over%20the%20years%20have%20had%20experience%20in%20quant%20finance%2C%20showing%20how%20successfully%20that%20skill%20set%20can%20translate.%20Chief%20Research%20Officer%20Mark%20Chen%20joined%20OpenAI%20in%202018%20after%20nearly%20seven%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-kevin-weil-mira-murati-great-bench-cto-abrupt-departure-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20quant%20research%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoam%20Brown%2C%20a%20top%20OpenAI%20researcher%20who%20joined%20in%202023%2C%20worked%20for%20a%20small%20quant-trading%20shop%20after%20graduating%20from%20Rutgers%20in%202008%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20didn't%20want%20my%20lifetime%20contribution%20to%20humanity%20to%20be%20making%20equity%20markets%20marginally%20more%20efficient%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fnoam-brown-8b785b62_thanks-for-your-interest-in-our-trading-talent-activity-7317942387018735617-JO3E%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAAAMV1kABUNgEoUDN7SsCVFa9ODk-vgOM3A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20LinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20promoting%20OpenAI's%20quant%20recruiting%20event.%20%26quot%3BTaking%20a%20pay%20cut%20to%20pursue%20AI%20research%20was%20my%20best%20life%20decision.%20Today%2C%20you%20don't%20even%20need%20to%20take%20a%20pay%20cut%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bad7d42b-95d3-4fa8-a1e4-1e44d886512c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBehind%20AI's%20multimillion-dollar%20offers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20some%20AI%20labs%20were%20offering%20machine-learning%20researchers%20with%20a%20couple%20years%20of%20experience%20up%20to%20%24750%2C000%2C%20including%20equity%2C%20according%20to%20a%20researcher%20who%20recently%20left%20a%20high-frequency%20trading%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20offers%20have%20now%20soared%20into%20the%20millions%3A%20The%20researcher%20says%20peers%20with%20similar%20work%20experience%20have%20received%20job%20offers%20from%20top%20AI%20labs%20ranging%20from%20roughly%20%241.5%20million%20to%20%243%20million%2C%20including%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researcher%20is%20considering%20a%20job%20at%20an%20AI%20lab%20%E2%80%94%20not%20necessarily%20for%20the%20AGI%20mission%20Altman%20trumpets%2C%20but%20because%20the%20economics%20seem%20too%20good%20to%20pass%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20offers%20have%20come%20up%20dramatically%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matt%20Moye%2C%20a%2020-year%20veteran%20of%20quant%20recruiting%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Monochrome%2C%20a%20search%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20Wall%20Street%20recruiters%20bemoaned%20shepherding%20quant%20candidates%20to%20final-stage%20interviews%20at%20top%20trading%20firms%20only%20to%20lose%20out%20to%20one%20of%20the%20buzzy%20top%20AI%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20recruiters%20said%20candidates%20frequently%20juggle%20offers%20from%20both%20sides.%20In%20one%20case%2C%20the%20offers%20were%20financially%20comparable%20%E2%80%94%20both%20low%20seven%20figures%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Anthropic%20offered%20a%20more%20enticing%20and%20broader%20mandate%20that%20was%20tantamount%20to%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20come%20play%20in%20AI%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said.%20(Anthropic%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20to%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20quant%20headhunter%20said%20that%20while%20he%20has%20firsthand%20knowledge%20of%20several%20quant%20candidates%20getting%20offers%20worth%20millions%20to%20leave%20for%20AI%2C%20he's%20also%20aware%20of%20tech%20candidates%20who%20have%20been%20getting%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20a%20point%20Zuckerberg's%20recent%20talent%20raid%20underscores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20quants%20aren't%20redefining%20the%20market%3B%20OpenAI%20redefined%20it%20before%20they%20went%20after%20quants%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20headhunter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1d16e32-45c3-46db-8eee-527f8642f261%5C%22%3EWhy%20AI%20labs%20see%20quants%20as%20natural%20fits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20the%20obvious%20overlap%20in%20skill%20set%20that%20makes%20quants%20attractive%20to%20AI%20labs.%20Quants%20already%20excel%20at%20mining%20vast%20data%20sets%20and%20engineering%20systems%20to%20unearth%20insights.%20As%20Carr%20puts%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20quantitative%20trading%20you%20need%20to%20be%20comfortable%20conducting%20research%20on%20large%20quantities%20of%20data%2C%20then%20you%20need%20to%20build%20a%20system%20that%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20any%20insights%20from%20that%20research.%20Sound%20familiar%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20high-octane%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intensity%20of%20the%20work%20is%20similar%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ho%2C%20the%20Perplexity%20cofounder.%20%26quot%3BTeams%20are%20very%20tight-knit%2C%20working%20super%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20breakneck%20pace%20of%20AI%20fundraising%20and%20hiring%20mirrors%20the%20non-stop%20grind%20of%20elite%20trading%20desks.%20One%20consultant%20who's%20worked%20with%20both%20Citadel%20and%20OpenAI%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20culture%20is%20not%20dissimilar.%20Citadel%20are%20famous%20for%20moving%20like%20a%20bullet%20train.%20Everyone%20is%20working%20every%20second.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20worlds%2C%20slight%20edges%20translate%20to%20enormous%20returns.%20Trading%20strategies%20decay%20fast%2C%20and%20AI%20models%20need%20constant%20updates%20to%20stay%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20trading%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20win%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20results%20directly%20tied%20to%20P%26amp%3BL%2C%20so%20in%20many%20ways%20it's%20always%20a%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moye.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20what%20we're%20seeing%20with%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20everyone%20knows%20it's%20a%20race.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20component%20that%20makes%20quants%20attractive%20is%20the%20lengthy%2C%20ubiquitous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-quant-battle-to-lock-up-traders-with-noncompetes-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoncompete%20clauses%20that%20systematic%20trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20firms%20put%20in%20employees'%20contracts%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20leaving%20for%20rivals%20with%20proprietary%20information.%20Because%20industry%20sit-outs%20can%20last%20two%20years%2C%20traders%20and%20researchers%20looking%20for%20a%20change%20have%20used%20the%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantrepreneurs-wall-street-quant-traders-build-silicon-valley-unicorn-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etest%20drive%20a%20career%20in%20Big%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20they%20don't%20like%20it%2C%20they%20can%20return%20to%20finance%20once%20their%20noncompete%20has%20lapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20they've%20worked%20in%20a%20hot%20new%20startup%20sector%20%E2%80%94%20a%20potentially%20risky%20bet.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-quants-leaving-for-silicon-valley-start-ups-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20was%20crypto%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20batch%20of%20AI%20startups%20offer%20a%20more%20compelling%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pitch%20is%20really%20net%20impact%20on%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Ho%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20continue%20farming%20markets%20for%20small%20amounts%20of%20edge%20on%20every%20trade.%20Or%20you%20can%20actually%20make%20a%20difference%20and%20make%20improvements%20in%20people's%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20AI%20products%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20direct%20impact%20on%20the%20user%20is%20so%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f972b2d0-bf2c-473c-b4c0-cfb4dee266d8%5C%22%3EDon't%20count%20Wall%20Street%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20has%20been%20here%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20long%20before%20Renaissance%20Technologies%20became%20the%20industry's%20most%20fabled%20quant%20hedge%20fund%2C%20founder%20Jim%20Simons%20was%20trying%20to%20lure%20a%20pair%20of%20IBM%20researchers%20who%20were%20working%20on%20nascent%20versions%20of%20large%20language%20models%20and%20speech%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBob%20Mercer%20and%20Peter%20Brown%20would%20become%20invaluable%20leaders%20at%20Renaissance%2C%20but%20Brown%2C%20who%20was%20the%20first%20grad%20student%20to%20study%20under%20AI%20godfather%20Geoffrey%20Hinton%2C%20was%20initially%20uninterested%20in%20joining%20%E2%80%94%20until%20Simons%20offered%20to%20double%20his%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%20offer%2C%20I%20came%20home.%20I%20took%20one%20look%20at%20our%20newborn%20daughter%20and%20realized%20I%20had%20no%20choice%20in%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%2C%20now%20CEO%20of%20Renaissance%2C%20said%20%