I%20studied%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-science-major-panic-masters-degree-graduate-school-job-market-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecomputer%20science%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20visual%20media%20at%20Duke.%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20tech.%20When%20I%20learned%20about%20the%20role%20of%20a%20product%20manager%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20cool.%20This%20is%20directly%20aligned%20with%20what%20I%20would%20do%20if%20I%20went%20into%20the%20corporate%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20and%20was%20accepted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-from-microsoft-twice-in-six-months-moving-forward-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20product%20manager%20intern%20during%20my%20junior%20year.%20I%20got%20a%20return%20offer%20from%20the%20internship%20for%20a%20hybrid%20role%20in%20Seattle%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20the%20role%2C%20I%20was%20really%20excited.%20My%20team%20was%20working%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-consolidate-teams-simplify-ai-copilot-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecurity%20Copilot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20a%20space%20where%20you%20can%20look%20at%20your%20entire%20security%20ecosystem%20in%20one%20place.%20I%20sometimes%20like%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20the%20ChatGPT%20of%20security%20within%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20it%20on%20and%20learn%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2267b8f7af-478c-4c8a-ae98-ff41bc83b010%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20work%20started%20out%20very%20rewarding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20joined%20full%20time%2C%20we%20hadn't%20even%20gotten%20the%20product%20to%20general%20availability%20(GA)%2C%20when%20all%20Microsoft%20customers%20can%20use%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20team%20moved%20and%20w