health-conscious%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rendering%20of%20an%20outdoor%20space%20at%20Pittsburgh%20International%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686432d0f748d8c055f4c104%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERendering%20of%20an%20outdoor%20space%20at%20Pittsburgh%20International%20Airport.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Pittsburgh%20International%20Airport%2FGensler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Pittsburgh%20International%20Airport%2C%20officials%20are%20also%20looking%20to%20take%20some%20of%20the%20stress%20out%20of%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20is%20undergoing%20a%20%241.7%20billion%20new%20terminal%20program%20that%20will%20add%20four%20outdoor%20terraces%2C%20two%20pre-security%20and%20two%20post-security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20aims%20to%20harness%20a%20%26quot%3Bbiophilic%26quot%3B%20design%20to%20bring%20nature%20to%20passengers%2C%20allowing%20flyers%20to%20grab%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%20and%20shake%20off%20some%20excess%20energy%20before%20boarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stress%20of%20uncertainty%20can%20make%20people%20anxious%2C%26quot%3B%20Christina%20Cassotis%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Pittsburgh%20International%20Airport%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20question%20is%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20create%20calm%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20passengers%20who%20could%20benefit%20from%20such%20spaces%2C%20with%20designers%20also%20keeping%20airport%20employees%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20ability%20to%20operate%20safely%20is%20100%25%20dependent%20on%20their%20frame%20of%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Young%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20airports%20to%20have%20added%20similar%20outdoor%20spaces%20include%20Austin-Bergstrom%20International%20Airport%2C%20Monterey%20Regional%20Airport%2C%20Long%20Beach%20Airport%2C%20Denver%20International%20Airport%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rendering%20of%20the%20planned%20dining%20terrace%20at%20San%20Diego%20International%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6870de89f748d8c055f56c35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERendering%20of%20the%20planned%20dining%20terrace%20at%20San%20Diego%20International%20Airport.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gensler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20travelers%20will%20no%20doubt%20delight%20in%20the%20opportunity%20to%20step%20outside%20of%20the%20terminal%2C%20for%20others%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20airside%20outdoor%20spaces%20might%20conjure%20up%20even%20more%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20airports%20and%20designers%20are%20taking%20a%20number%20of%20precautions%20to%20minimize%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPost-security%20outdoor%20spaces%20require%20careful%20planning%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20safety%20and%20security%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20Trupiano%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20includes%20physical%20barriers%20and%20screening%20processes%20to%20prevent%20the%20transfer%20of%20prohibited%20items%20from%20non-secure%20to%20secure%20areas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20design%20strategies%20to%20mitigate%20the%20risk%20of%20foreign%20object%20debris%20near%20aircraft%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAviation%20security%20expert%20Jeffrey%20Price%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20significant%20security%20measure%26quot%3B%20is%20often%20a%20plexiglass%20wall%20that%20extends%20around%20eight%20to%2010%20feet%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20these%20were%20also%20made%20%26quot%3Bas%20seamless%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20them%20difficult%20to%20climb%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECCTV%20is%20also%20often%20in%20place%20to%20monitor%