house%20leases%20had%20been%20signed%20in%20the%20past%20month%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20totaling%20about%202.2%20million%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20has%20had%20a%20significant%20uptick%20over%20the%20last%20month%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20that%20that%20continues%2C%26quot%3B%20Kossar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrookfield-warehouse-acquisition-andy-smith-cheaper-rents-tariffs-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752483601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687168ed3d5881a51c1d3675%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrookfield-warehouse-acquisition-andy-smith-cheaper-rents-tariffs-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brookfield%20bets%20on%20older%2C%20lower-cost%20warehouses%20as%20trade%20uncertainties%20and%20oversupply%20cloud%20the%20outlook%20for%20industrial%20storage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dgeiger%40businessinsider.com%20(Daniel%20Geiger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrookfield-warehouse-acquisition-andy-smith-cheaper-rents-tariffs-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Demis%20Hassabis%20became%20Google's%20best%20superpower%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20maybe%20its%20next%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223637%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Demis%20Hassabis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684ade3e3d5881a51c1b4661%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222425%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeepMind%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis.%3Cp%3EJack%20Taylor%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20SXSW%20London%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Google's%20most%20powerful%20leaders%20is%20someone%20who%20long%20tried%20to%20distance%20his%20company%20from%20the%20search%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20mastermind%20and%20chess%20wiz%20Demis%20Hassabis%2C%20who%20founded%20DeepMind%20and%20later%20sold%20it%20to%20Google%20in%202014%2C%20has%20been%20propelled%20into%20the%20center%20of%20Google's%20universe%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%20amid%20the%20frenzied%20race%20for%20AI%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20trying%20to%20create%20more%20independence%20for%20DeepMind%20%E2%80%94%20shielding%20the%20AI%20research%20lab%20from%20the%20search%20giant%20%E2%80%94%20Hassabis%20was%20thrust%20into%20the%20belly%20of%20the%20beast%20in%202023%20when%20Google%20merged%20DeepMind%20with%20its%20internal%20AI%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20company%20insiders%20close%20to%20Hassabis%20say%20he%20is%20destined%20for%20even%20greater%20heights%20that%20may%20give%20him%20more%20control%20over%20the%20powerful%20AI%20technology%20he%20builds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20possibly%20one%20day%20lead%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20he's%20interested%20in%20those%20ambitions%20is%20another%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Hassabis%20hoped%20the%20AI%20race%20would%20be%20one%20led%20by%20academics%20and%20scientists%20in%20research%20labs%2C%20with%20international%20organizations%20to%20prevent%20AI's%20misuse%20and%20to%20map%20humanity's%20path%20through%20a%20new%20era%20of%20technological%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20now%20faces%20the%20pressures%20of%20pushing%20the%20frontiers%20of%20AI%20and%20also%20building%20it%20into%20Google's%20commercial%20products.%20He's%20wrangling%20a%206%2C000-plus%20team%20inside%20Google's%20AI%20engine%20room%20that%20has%20accrued%20increasingly%20more%20power%20and%20talent%E2%80%94Google%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-planned-acquisition-windsurf-called-off-ceo-poached-google-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDeepMind%20just%20poached%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20core%20team%20of%20the%20AI%20coding%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevelopers-redefined-builders-ai-windsurf-ceo-varun-mohan-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWindsurf%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20rival%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-battle-over-microsofts-access-to-openais-technology-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20previously%20planned%20to%20acquire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20have%20never%20been%20higher%3A%20He%20has%20to%20keep%20Google%20ahead%20of%20corporate%20rivals%20and%20keep%20the%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-deepseek-r1-china-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eahead%20of%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20rise%20reminds%20me%20of%20Sundar's%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20longtime%20Google%20employee%20who%20has%20worked%20closely%20with%20Hassabis%20and%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20you%20started%20hearing%20this%20name%20Sundar%20internally%2C%20and%20he%20kept%20having%20more%20and%20more%20responsibility%2C%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20he%20was%20the%20CEO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDemis'%20rise%20has%20been%20similar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20added.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20he's%20responsible%20for%20what%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20important%20team%20at%20Google%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20company%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einsiders%20for%20this%20story.%20They%20described%20how%20Google%20tapped%20its%20ultimate%20AI%20weapon%20in%20Hassabis%2C%20who%20has%20the%20makings%20of%20a%20CEO%20%E2%80%94%20and%20whose%20ascent%20within%20Google%20has%20come%20with%20trade-offs.%20Google%20declined%20to%20make%20Hassabis%20available%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2886dda-812c-425c-9760-799fdfef202c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle's%20AI%20battle%20plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20British-born%20cognitive%20neuroscience%20Ph.D.%2C%20Hassabis%20cofounded%20DeepMind%20in%202010%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20one%20day%20creating%20a%20general-purpose%20artificial%20intelligence.%20In%202014%2C%20Hassabis%20sold%20the%20company%20to%20Google%20for%20%24650%20million%20with%20a%20caveat%3A%20It%20would%20create%20an%20AI%20ethics%20board%20that%20would%20limit%20how%20Google%20could%20use%20DeepMind's%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20Hassabis%20would%20take%20this%20further%2C%20fighting%20to%20create%20legal%20thicker%20walls%20between%20his%20lab%20and%20the%20search%20giant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepmind-secret-plot-break-away-from-google-project-watermelon-mario-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20DeepMind's%20leaders%20worried%20that%20their%20AI%20would%20be%20used%20for%20military%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20ChatGPT%20became%20a%20hit%20in%20late%202022%2C%20Google%20leaders%20ordered%20several%20pivots%20inside%20the%20company%20to%20address%20the%20potential%20threat%20to%20the%20search%20giant's%20business.%20In%20DeepMind%20earlier%20that%20year%2C%20Hassabis%20had%20told%20staff%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20reorient%20his%20lab%20toward%20building%20an%20AI%20assistant.%20One%20former%20employee%20said%20they%20were%20confused%20at%20the%20time%20as%20to%20how%20DeepMind%20could%20ever%20build%20something%20that%20would%20directly%20compete%20with%20Google's%20own%20Assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20soon%20didn't%20matter.%20In%202023%2C%20after%20talks%20to%20secure%20DeepMind's%20independence%20failed%2C%20Pichai%20announced%20the%20unit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-big-shakeup-gives-more-power-to-deepmind-pixel-leaders-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewould%20fuse%20with%20Google's%20internal%20AI%20lab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20merged%20their%20AI%20assistant%20efforts.%20Google%20was%20caught%20flat-footed%20by%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20needed%20a%20battle%20plan.%20Google%20DeepMind%2C%20a%20fusion%20of%20the%20company's%20two%20premier%20AI%20labs%2C%20was%20the%20answer%2C%20and%20Hassabis%20is%20in%20its%20driver's%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20has%20done%20more%20managing%20than%20ever%20since.%20Merging%20DeepMind%20with%20the%20Brain%20team%20from%20Google%20Research%20meant%20Hassabis%20had%20to%20oversee%20the%20merging%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etwo%20units%20that%20historically%20had%20behaved%20more%20like%20competitors%20than%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20before%20the%20merger%2C%20things%20had%20gotten%20so%20bad%20between%20both%20organizations%20trying%20to%20scoop%20one%20another%20that%20Hassabis%20had%20DeepMind's%20code%20locked%20so%20it%20wasn't%20visible%20to%20Google%20employees.%20Now%2C%20bringing%20them%20together%20meant%20deciding%20who%20should%20sit%20under%20whom%2C%20leading%20to%20some%20political%20infighting%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20people%20who%20were%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepMind%20also%20used%20different%20programming%20technology%20than%20Google%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decision%20Hassabis%20made%20to%20avoid%20dependencies%20on%20Google%20teams%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20the%20merger%20posed%20a%20large%20technical%20challenge.%20A%20Google%20spokesperson%20said%20these%20issues%20had%20since%20been%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrusting%20Hassabis%20into%20the%20driver's%20seat%20gave%20him%20more%20power%20but%20less%20control.%20For%20example%2C%20Hassabis%20has%20had%20to%20change%20his%20stance%20on%20what%20were%20once%20red%20lines%3A%20In%20February%202024%2C%20Google%20dropped%20a%20pledge%20made%20in%202018%20not%20to%20use%20its%20AI%20for%20military%20purposes%2C%20following%20the%20rest%20of%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Hassabis%20cosigned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Ftechnology%2Fai%2Fresponsible-ai-2024-report-ongoing-work%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20defending%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20we%20first%20published%20our%20AI%20Principles%20in%202018%2C%20the%20AI%20field%20has%20evolved%20substantially%2C%20and%20we've%20updated%20our%20Principles%20to%20more%20effectively%20meet%20the%20environment%20of%20today.%20Our%20core%20commitment%20remains%3A%20benefits%20must%20substantially%20outweigh%20harms%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Google%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20merger%20process%2C%20dozens%20of%20DeepMind%20employees%20left%20for%20other%20labs%2C%20pushed%20out%20by%20internal%20politics%20and%20pulled%20away%20by%20a%20red-hot%20AI%20job%20market.%20A%20pullback%20on%20publishing%20certain%20types%20of%20research%20also%20rankled%20some%20staff%2C%20insiders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20joined%20an%20academic%20research%20lab%20and%20suddenly%20they're%20being%20asked%20to%20build%20products%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20what%20they%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20DeepMind%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20were%20excited%20by%20how%20Google%20had%20been%20shaken%20out%20of%20its%20slumber%2C%20especially%20when%20cofounder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sergey-brin-back-from-retirement-to-build-gemini-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESergey%20Brin%3C%2Fa%3E%20returned%20to%20the%20trenches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20merger%20has%20required%20Hassabis%20to%20play%20a%20hand%20in%20the%20sorts%20of%20Google%20politicking%20DeepMind%20had%20for%20a%20long%20time%20avoided%20to%20some%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20Studio%2C%20Google's%20AI%20developer%20platform%2C%20was%20previously%20part%20of%20Google's%20Cloud%20organization%20and%20became%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20when%20teams%20working%20on%20Google's%20other%20AI%20cloud%20platform%2C%20Vertex%2C%20saw%20AI%20Studio%20as%20a%20competitor%20internally%2C%20according%20to%20two%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20The%20AI%20Studio%20team%20moved%20to%20Google%20DeepMind%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20resolution%20that%20Hassabis%20helped%20broker%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20both%20those%20products%20serve%20different%20purposes%20and%20that%20DeepMind%20and%20Google%20had%20historically%20collaborated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20many%20shared%20views%20and%20ways%20of%20working%20between%20the%20two%20teams%2C%20and%20the%20merger%20has%20been%20very%20smooth%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Demis%20Hassabis%20on%20stage%20at%20Google%20I%2FO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686b93233d5881a51c1cc3be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHassabis%20onstage%20at%20Google%20I%2FO.%3Cp%3ECAMILLE%20COHEN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis'%20new%20position%20has%20some%20employees%20wondering%20if%20he%20is%20being%20groomed%20to%20succeed%20Pichai%20and%20if%20the%20CEO%20chair%20could%20give%20him%20the%20level%20of%20control%20over%20Google's%20AI%20he%20has%20always%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20if%20Google%20transforms%20into%20the%20AI-first%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsundar-pichai-ai-first-world-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPichai%20promised%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ultimate%20form%20of%20Google%2C%20as%20cofounder%20Larry%20Page%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-apple-building-blocks-chatgpt-data-centers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonce%20saw%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Hassabis%20is%20the%20smartest