https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-ceo-wins-nobel-prize-chemistry-demis-hassabis-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Nobel%20Prize%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20work%20on%20DeepMind's%20protein%20folding%20project%2C%20and%20even%20slipped%20in%20a%20knighthood%20for%20%26quot%3Bservices%20to%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20bestowed%20upon%20him%20by%20King%20Charles%20III.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20have%20worked%20with%20Hassabis%20describe%20him%20as%20a%20double%20threat%3A%20He's%20incredibly%20smart%20and%20can%20dive%20deep%20into%20technical%20topics.%20He%20also%20has%20the%20charm%20and%20charisma%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20make%20them%20believe%20AGI%20will%20happen%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20he'll%20be%20the%20one%20to%20lead%20them%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevang%20Agrawal%2C%20a%20former%20DeepMinder%2C%20recalled%20how%20he%20was%20studying%20for%20his%20undergraduate%20degree%20when%20Hassabis%20visited%20his%20university%20and%20gave%20the%20students%20a%20demo%20where%20an%20AI%20system%20used%20reinforcement%20learning%20to%20play%20Atari%20games.%20Agrawal%20was%20sold%20on%20the%20mission%2C%20and%20a%20few%20years%20later%2C%20he%20was%20working%20for%20Hassabis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Demis%20has%20this%20really%20brilliant%20quality%20about%20him%2C%20to%20talk%20in%20an%20inspirational%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Agrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDemis%20is%20very%20good%20at%20convincing%20you%20that%20you%20and%20him%20together%20are%20going%20to%20change%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20former%20DeepMind%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20can%20also%20be%20fiercely%20competitive%2C%20colleagues%20and%20friends%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hassabis%20receiving%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%20Chemistry%20in%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.co