26quot%3BThey%20needed%20to%20raise%20it%20to%20work%20on%20something%20that%20seemed%20crazy%20to%20most%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20cofounder%20Page%20convinced%20Hassabis%20to%20sell%2C%20promising%20to%20give%20DeepMind%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20independence.%20The%20arrangement%20allowed%20DeepMind%20to%20continue%20its%20research%20without%20being%20part%20of%20Google's%20corporate%20bureaucracy%2C%20while%20also%20giving%20the%20company%20access%20to%20what%20would%20become%20more%20valuable%20than%20anything%20else%3A%20compute%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhereas%20today%20there's%20enough%20interest%20where%20you%20can%20raise%20enough%20money%20without%20giving%20away%20the%20whole%20company%2C%20so%20they%20get%20to%20retain%20control.%20I%20can%20just%20imagine%20that's%20how%20Demis%20would%20prefer%20things%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20in%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204338a07-8255-48ea-9623-02c20cecef2f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemis%20Hassabis%20is%20on%20the%20quest%20for%20AGI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20now%20walks%20a%20difficult%20line%20between%20his%20own%20interests%20regarding%20AGI%20and%20those%20of%20Google's%20shareholders.%20Running%20Google's%20control%20room%20now%20means%20pushing%20the%20frontiers%20of%20AI%20research%20while%20infusing%20it%20into%20the%20company's%20suite%20of%20products%2C%20from%20Search%20to%20Maps%20to%20Workspace.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20team%20has%20absorbed%20more%20parts%20of%20Google%2C%20including%20the%20team%20for%20its%20Gemini%20chatbot%2C%20consolidating%20more%20power%20under%20Hassabis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-publishing-less-confidential-ai-research-to-compete-with-openai-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20DeepMind%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20scaled%20back%20the%20types%20of%20papers%20it%20publishes%