t%20understand%20how%20you%20can%20want%20to%20go%20to%20grad%20school%3B%20we're%20building%20this%20company.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20next%20move%20shaped%20the%20course%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamat%20sent%20a%20cold%20reach%20out%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsergey-brin-career-life-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESergey%20Brin%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20asking%20the%20Google%20cofounder%20for%20advice.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20he%20didn't%20know%20Brin%20personally%2C%20but%20he%20had%20read%20Brin's%20research%20papers%20and%20held%20a%20deep%20level%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%201999%203%20a.m.%20email%2C%26quot%3B%20Samat%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20asked%20Brin%2C%20%26quot%3B'What%20would%20you%20do%20in%20this%20situation%3F%20I'm%20sure%20you%20had%20this%20wrestle%20with%20this%20grad%20school%20decision.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamat%20said%20that%20Brin%20answered%20a%20minute%20later%20saying%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20problem%20and%20inviting%20him%20to%20Google's%20offices.%20Samat%20then%20went%20to%20visit%20Brin%20and%20they%20talked%20for%20a%20bit%20before%20the%20cofounder%20%26quot%3Bparaded%20one%20engineering%20person%20after%20another%20into%20the%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20ended%20up%20doing%20the%20Google%20interview%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20Samat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20impromptu%20interview%20rounds%2C%20Samat%20said%20Brin%20offered%20him%20a%20job%20at%20the%20search%20giant.%20While%20Samat%20said%20he%20was%20flattered%20by%20the%20offer%2C%20he%20told%20Brin%20he%20was%20committed%20to%20his%20startup%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave%20his%20cofounders%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrin%20respected%20the%20decision%20but%20gave%20him%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%3A%20If%20he%20was%20going%20to%20pursue%20his%20own%20company%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20do%20it%20