6quot%3BYeah%2C%20it's%20vile%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied%2C%20in%20a%20tone%20that%20actually%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20it's%20the%20best%20thing%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20For%20him%20it%20is%3A%20As%20long%20as%20people%20use%20air%20conditioning%2C%20their%20air%20ducts%20will%20always%20get%20dirty%2C%20and%20as%20long%20as%20there%20are%20dirty%20air%20ducts%2C%20there%20will%20always%20be%20business%20for%20Atlantic.%20And%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20dirty%20air%20ducts%20out%20there.%20After%20showing%20me%20around%20the%20office%2C%20Schweber%20took%20me%20out%20to%20a%20day%20care%20center%20that%20had%20hired%20Atlantic%20for%20the%20day%20because%20of%20a%20smell%20wafting%20from%20the%20AC.%20By%20the%20time%20we%20got%20there%2C%20three%20technicians%20had%20vacuumed%20out%20a%20ton%20of%20dust%20and%20debris%20from%20the%20building's%20air%20ducts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20culprit%20of%20the%20odor%2C%20a%20dead%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Air%20Ducts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68713aac85e81483682dddd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20many%20before%20and%20after%20photos%20of%20air%20ducts%20that%20Schweber%20gleefully%20showed%20me%20on%20his%20phone.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dan%20Schweber%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20all%20goes%20according%20to%20plan%2C%20Schweber%20is%20in%20for%20a%20big%20payout.%20Of%20the%20search%20entrepreneurs%20who%20eventually%20sell%20their%20business%2C%20just%20under%20a%20quarter%20of%20them%20get%20nothing%3B%20another%2027%25%20get%20less%20than%20%244%20million%20in%20equity%3B%2028%25%20get%20%244%20million%20to%20%2410%20million%3B%20and%20the%20luckiest%2018%25%20get%20more%20than%20%2410%20million.%20That%20eight-digit%20reward%20is%20what%20every%20searcher%20dreams%20of.%20Schweber%20wants%20a%20beach%20house%20and%20a%20Bent