k-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20engineer%20who%20returned%20to%20her%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20place%20is%20%E2%80%98Cafe%20Aarambh%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98beginning%E2%80%99%20in%20Hindi.%20It%20was%20founded%20by%2027-year-old%20Nishtha%20Chauhan%2C%20an%20electronics%20and%20communications%20engineer%20who%20left%20a%20promising%20career%20in%20aerospace%20to%20return%20to%20the%20earth%2C%20quite%20literally.%20Instead%20of%20the%20conventional%20corporate%20path%2C%20Nishtha%20chose%20to%20till%20the%20soil%2C%20grind%20millets%20and%20compost%20kitchen%20scraps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20journey%20is%20not%20a%20spontaneous%20detour.%20Raised%20in%20a%20modest%20Gujarati%20household%2C%20she%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20the%20wisdom%20of%20her%20grandfather%2C%20a%20millet%20practitioner%20who%20firmly%20believed%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F271562%2Fchennai-woman-sells-ready-to-eat-snack-mixes-from-ancient-grains%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoodness%20of%20ancient%20grains%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(finger%20millet)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sorghum)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pearl%20millet)%2C%20and%20little%20millet.%20Mealtimes%20at%20home%20were%20simple%20and%20wholesome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20grown%20up%20accustomed%20to%20seeing%20all%20the%20kitchen%E2%80%99s%20wet%20waste%20carefully%20composted.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20did%20not%20think%20much%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20once%20I%20became%20an%20adult%20and%20looked%20around%20me%2C%20I%20began%20to%20realise%20just%20how%20deeply%20those%20habits%20were%20ingrained%20in%20me%2C%20and%20how%20important%20they%20really%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20Lalbhai%20Dalpatbhai%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Nishtha%20joined%20Azista%20Aerospace%2C%20where%20she%20worked%20on%20satellite%20payloads%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%20It%20was%20an%20exciting%20work%20which%20was%20intellectually%20demanding%20and%20high-profile.%20But%20amid%20the%20sterile%20labs%20and%20long%20hours%2C%20she%20felt%20increasingly%20disconnected.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nishtha%20Chauhan%20always%20wanted%20to%20start%20a%20food%20business%20but%20she%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20can%20help%20the%20society%20and%20the%20environment%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467608%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENishtha%20Chauhan%20always%20wanted%20to%20start%20a%20food%20business%2C%20but%20she%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20could%20help%20society%20and%20the%20environment%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20something%20of%20my%20own%20in%20the%20food%20sector.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20want%20it%20to%20be%20just%20another%20cafe%20serving%20pizzas%20or%20fast%20food.%20The%20market%20is%20already%20full%20of%20that.%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20would%20not%20only%20nourish%20people%20but%20also%20give%20back%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20support%20our%20local%20farmers.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20rooted%20in%20purpose%20and%20not%20just%20profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20COVID-19%20waves%20hit%2C%20which%20brought%20a%20pause%20to%20her%20usual%20routine%20and%20gave%20her%20a%20chance%20to%20rethink%20everything.%20As%20she%20watched%20the%20world%20buckle%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20disease%2C%20lifestyle%20disorders%2C%20and%20climate%20anxiety%2C%20she%20could%20not%20shake%20the%20feeling%20that%20food%20lay%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20it%20all.%20She%20began%20researching%20nutrition%2C%20agroecology%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20neglected%20food%20heritage.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20research%20soon%20led%20her%20to%20focus%20on%20millets%20and%20organically%20grown%20vegetables%2C%20all%20tied%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20zero-waste%20lifestyle.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20more%20I%20read%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20how%20powerful%20these%20grains%20are%2C%20not%20just%20for%20our%20health%20but%20for%20the%20planet%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CMillets%20require%20far%20less%20water%20and%20pesticides%20than%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250058%2Ffarmer-innovation-chintala-venkat-reddy-telangana-farmer-padma-shri-awardee-vitamin-d-rice-wheat-patent-wipo-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econventional%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20resilient%2C%20nutritious%2C%20and%20connected%20to%20our%20heritage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20understanding%20birthed%20a%20desire%20to%20bring%20these%20elements%20together%20in%20a%20thoughtful%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECooking%20with%20a%20conscience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20left%20her%20full-time%20engineering%20job%20in%20early%202021%20to%20focus%20entirely%20on%20her%20research%20and%20vision.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20daunting%20to%20step%20away%20from%20the%20security%20of%20a%20steady%20career%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20dedicate%20myself%20fully%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20impactful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20months%20went%20into%20experimentation%20and%20learning.%20The%20entrepreneur%20imagined%20a%20place%20where%20people%20could%20rediscover%20millets%20and%20traditional%20grains%20not%20as%20old-fashioned%20staples%20but%20as%20exciting%2C%20delicious%2C%20and%20sustainable%20food%20options.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20a%20space%20that%20would%20inspire%20people%20to%20rethink%20their%20choices%2C%20enjoy%20healthy%20food%20that%20tastes%20great%2C%20and%20understand%20the%20story%20behind%20every%20dish%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092807.982_11zon-1752206303.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20more%20than%202%2C000%20young%20students%20have%20attended%20the%20healthy%20eating%20workshop%20conducted%20by%20Nishtha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092807.982_11zon-1752206303.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092807.982_11zon-1752206303-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092807.982_11zon-1752206303-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092807.982_11zon-1752206303-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092807.982_11zon-1752206303-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467615%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20more%20than%202%2C000%20young%20students%20have%20attended%20the%20healthy%20eating%20workshop%20conducted%20by%20Nishtha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20she%20opened%20Cafe%20Aarambh%20in%20the%20leafy%20premises%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Environment%20Education%20(CEE)%20in%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20Thaltej%20area.%20Modest%20in%20scale%20but%20ambitious%20in%20philosophy%2C%20the%20cafe%20runs%20on%20a%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%20sourcing%2C%20zero%20waste%2C%20and%20a%20return%20to%20traditional%20and%20wholesome%20eating.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20carefully%20designed%20seasonal%20menu%20features%2015%20to%2020%20millet-based%20dishes%20that%20rotate%20based%20on%20seasonal%20availability%2C%20such%20as%20soft%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20dosas%2C%20pearl%20bhel%2C%20millet%20momos%2C%20a%3C%2Fem%3End%20a%20popular%20take%20on%20the%20classic%3Cem%3E%20vada%20pav%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eserved%20in%20freshly%20baked%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20buns.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meals%20are%20presented%20with%20the%20same%20thoughtfulness%20that%20goes%20into%20their%20preparation.%20Each%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F415426%2Fspice-up-foods-homemade-ready-eat-preservative-free-food-homemakers-meals-travellers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeal%20offers%20the%20comfort%20of%20a%20home-cooked%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20meals%20are%20served%20in%20glassware%2C%20completely%20avoiding%20plastic%20or%20any%20disposable%20clutter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20rare%20occasions%2C%20when%20single-use%20containers%20are%20needed%2C%20such%20as%20during%20takeaways%20or%20when%20food%20is%20served%20at%20external%20events%2C%20the%20cafe%20opts%20for%20biodegradable%20alternatives.%20Plates%20and%20bowls%20made%20from%20areca%20leaves%20or%20bagasse%2C%20both%20fully%20compostable%2C%20guarantee%20that%20convenience%20never%20comes%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20environment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20prefer%20to%20keep%20the%20menu%20small%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nishtha.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20walk%20into%20most%20cafes%2C%20you%20see%20pages%20and%20pages%20of%20options.%20But%20here%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20dishes%20that%20are%20nourishing%20and%20connected%20to%20local%20traditions.%20It%20also%20means%20we%20avoid%20over-ordering%20ingredients%20or%20wasting%20what%20we%20cook.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EZero%20waste%20and%20maximum%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20intention%20carries%20through%20into%20the%20kitchen%2C%20where%20food%20is%20prepared%20each%20morning%20in%20limited%20quantities.%20Rather%20than%20guessing%20large%20numbers%2C%20the%20team%20carefully%20estimates%20how%20much%20will%20be%20needed%2C%20based%20on%20previous%20experience%20and%20the%20season%E2%80%99s%20demand.%20If%20a%20particular%20dish%20runs%20out%20before%20the%20day%20ends%2C%20it%20is%20removed%20from%20the%20menu%2C%20and%20no%20extra%20batches%20are%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20is%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20wastage%20and%20to%20create%20a%20sense%20of%20anticipation%20and%20appreciation%20among%20the%20cafe%E2%80%99s%20regulars.%20People%20come%20to%20the%20cafe%20not%20just%20to%20eat%2C%20but%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20system%20that%20values%20quality%20over%20quantity%2C%20and%20freshness%20over%20convenience.%20Each%20decision%2C%20from%20portion%20sizes%20to%20how%20leftovers%20are%20handled%2C%20reflects%20a%20larger%20ethic%20of%20responsibility.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424409%2Fwhere-unsegregated-kitchen-waste-goes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleftover%20vegetable%20peels%20and%20wet%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20turned%20into%20compost%2C%20feeding%20the%20small%20but%20spirited%20kitchen%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095600.126_11zon-1752207979.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Cafe%20Aarambh%2C%20food%20is%20prepared%20in%20small%20batches%20so%20that%20there%20is%20less%20wastage%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095600.126_11zon-1752207979.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095600.126_11zon-1752207979-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T095600.126_11zon-1752207979-