2Fa%3E%C2%A0forged%20his%20own%20path.%20As%20a%20wildlife%20researcher%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20he%20framed%20a%20question%20that%20would%20address%20the%20fundamental%20challenge%20of%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20reconcile%20the%20notion%20of%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20local%20communities%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%2C%20particularly%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20to%20these%20elusive%20creatures%3F%20To%20answer%20this%20question%2C%20he%20established%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%20in%202000%20to%20promote%20local%20efforts%20towards%20community-based%20conservation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20taking%20a%20variety%20of%20steps%20to%20help%20local%20farmers%20and%20nomads%20protect%20their%20livestock%20from%20snow%20leopards%2C%20thus%20preventing%20man-animal%20conflicts%2C%20he%20also%20pioneered%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20models%20of%20eco-tourism%20with%20conservation-linked%20homestays%20located%20in%20critical%20snow%20leopard%20habitats%20and%20along%20popular%20trekking%20routes.%20These%20successful%20models%20of%20community-based%20tourism%20in%20the%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20Sham%20region%2C%20and%20Zanskar%20still%20stand%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20tragically%20passed%20away%20at%20the%20age%20of%20just%2042%20in%202011%20due%20to%20a%20deteriorating%20neurological%20condition%20but%20not%20before%20leaving%20behind%20a%20stellar%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-78-1752236000.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fateh%20Singh%20Rathore%20(L)%20(Image%20courtesy%20Wikimedia%20Commons)%20and%20Kailash%20Sankhala%20(R)%20(Source%3A%20Amit%20Sankhala)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%