antola%20is%20well-suited%20for%20warm%2C%20humid%20weather%20and%20requires%20very%20little%20intervention%20once%20established.%20With%20the%20onset%20of%20monsoon%20providing%20ideal%20conditions%20for%20germination%20and%20growth%2C%20now%20is%20an%20excellent%20time%20to%20plant%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20step-by-step%20guide%20outlines%20everything%20beginners%20need%20to%20know%20%E2%80%94%20from%20sourcing%20seeds%20and%20preparing%20soil%20to%20supporting%20the%20vine%20and%20harvesting%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20grow%20kantola%20in%2010%20easy%20steps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Source%20the%20right%20seeds%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20by%20getting%20quality%20%3Cem%3Ekantola%3C%2Fem%3E%20seeds%20or%20tuber%20roots%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20agro%20shop%2C%20or%20reliable%20online%20vendor.%20Look%20for%20heirloom%20or%20indigenous%20varieties.%20Kantola%20can%20be%20grown%20from%20seeds%20or%20from%20tuberous%20roots%3B%20tubers%20sprout%20quicker%2C%20but%20seeds%20are%20more%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-500x910.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-500x910.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-165x300.jpg%20165w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964-150x273.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F612Z27UTnOL._SL1382_-1752155964.jpg%20759w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467403%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Choose%20the%20right%20spot%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKantola%20loves%20warm%20and%20humid%20weather%2C%20and%20monsoon%20provides%20that%20naturally.%20Select%20a%20sunny%20to%20partially%20shaded%20area%2C%20it%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F443287%2Fgrow-brinjal-at-home-monsoon-guide-growing-in-pots-small-space-step-by-step-guide-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20ground%2C%20on%20your%20terrace%2C%20or%20in%20large%20pots.%20%3C%2Fa%3EMake%20sure%20there%E2%80%99s%20enough%20space%20for%20the%20vine%20to%20spread%20and%20climb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Prepare%20the%20soil%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoamy%2C%20well-drained%20soil%20works%20best%20for%20Kantola.%20Mix%20garden%20soil%20with%20compost%20or%20cow%20dung%20to%20enrich%20it.%20Add%20sand%20or%20cocopeat%20if%20your%20soil%20retains%20too%20much%20water.%20Kantola%20hates%20waterlogging%2C%20so%20good%20drainage%20is%20a%20must.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Soak%20before%20you%20sow%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20using%20seeds%2C%20soak%20them%20in%20water%20for%2024%20hours%20to%20speed%20up%20germination.%20If%20using%20tubers%2C%20plant%20them%20directly%2C%20but%20ensure%20they%20are%20healthy%20and%20disease-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Planting%20time%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20time%20to%20plant%20%3Cem%3Ekantola%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20monsoon%2C%20ideally%20June%20to%20early%20July.%20Sow%20seeds%2Ftubers%20one%20inch%20deep%20and%20about%201.5%20to%20two%20feet%20apart.%20In%20pots%2C%20use%20at%20least%2012-inch%